{"tid":580654,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"搭車永遠唔會同呢五類人坐","createTime":"2018-03-04T16:11:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T00:37:12.000Z","uid":143774,"like":43,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bb18c1cf5ebbf8b06cad84a74f390e66ea06ffce","tid":580654,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:11:01.000Z","msg":"1) 煙鏟<br />\n<br />\n恨不得佢快啲死，最好死之前幾年，係醫院度吊下命<br />\n個陣嘅煙除真係難聞到嘔，仲要坐隔離都好明顯，呢班垃圾通常係上車前仲會食返枝先，煙味就真係新舊交雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聞到人勁作嘔<br />\n<br />\n2) 師奶<br />\n<br />\n通常幾袋野，幾隻師奶聚埋一齊，成程車圍威喂，十足十開籠雀，有時朝早/收工想靜下都無可能<br />\n<br />\n3) 廢老<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4) 細佬仔<br />\n<br />\n好似啪撚咗藥，無時停係咁爬，隨時幫佢地教仔<br />\n<br />\n5) 大隻佬/肥佬<br />\n<br />\n不如我俾半價好無，橫掂你都坐咗1.5 個位<br />\n再講，肥人一出汗就好撚臭，尤其係肥佬<br />\n<br />\nPS 淨係同靚女坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f6a982447c1f4a550149fbdcab3261c6720ea7c","tid":580654,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:13:04.000Z","msg":"根據以上列表<br />\n我都唔會同你坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed927e98a3928bee141133ac27ffd7f8420835b7","tid":580654,"uid":132219,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:15:14.000Z","msg":"仲有毒撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n即係你呀樓主"},{"pid":"2d8f594e550dfabea9985c10f9e1fd3a1180ea0f","tid":580654,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T16:18:36.000Z","msg":"上層同無自知之明肥仔坐真係好痛苦<br />\n佢地又唔縮埋自己坐入d 次次坐到腰都痛"},{"pid":"3ed552951d9a11568a3fc20ae7cda360b8d7de22","tid":58